  "reference_number": "RUS1336",
  "remarks": "\nNigina ZAIROVA (hereafter ZAIROVA) is an involved person under the Russia (Sanctions) (EU Exit) Regulations 2019 on the basis of the following grounds:  \n(1) ZAIROVA is associated with Mikhail FRIDMAN including by obtaining a financial benefit or other material benefit from FRIDMAN. \n(2) ZAIROVA is acting on behalf of or at the direction of a person who is or has been so involved in obtaining a benefit from the Government of Russia, namely FRIDMAN. \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
